Is anyone still afraid of Friday the thirteenth? It
seems a very quaint superstition in these modern
times. I think most people would rather just get on
with their lives. To that end, I'm going to cast fear
to the wind, bust open the 7thcol@bungie.com
mailbag and read about what's happening to those
lucky enough to be part of the Seventh Column.
